A labels for all charts\\n- Keyboard navigation support\\n- Color contrast >4.5:1\\n- Screen reader-friendly data tables\\n\\n## Existing Infrastructure\\n- `frontend/src/pages/AgentMetricsDashboard.tsx` - Main dashboard page\\n- `frontend/src/components/metrics/` - Reusable metric components (to be created)\\n- Theme-aware styling (dark/light mode support)\\n", "size": 1794, "s3Key": "workflow-runs/81567f3d-3765-463a-be99-56370c51b42f/components/1acb6fcd-815d-4b03-aeff-63b0b522133a/uiux-design-st2.md", "format": "markdown", "filename": "uiux-design-st2.md", "language": null, "mimeType": "application/markdown", "uploadedAt": "2025-11-17T12:37:45.843Z", "artifactType": "report"}]
1e60d624-4db3-41e9-ae70-0af1be9618c0	81567f3d-3765-463a-be99-56370c51b42f	89e6cc43-7bcb-41aa-9173-3dcd1c9cfa46	\N	completed	f	{"focus": "OTEL metrics collection, ComponentRun schema, ingestion services", "storyKey": "ST-2", "storyTitle": "Comprehensive Agent Statistics Tracking System"}	{"criticalGaps": 4, "artifactStored": "context-exploration-st2.md", "filesIdentified": 20, "recommendations": 4}	\N	0	0	3500	46	\N	1	\N	\N	{}	{}	\N	\N	\N	\N	0	1	0	[]	\N	0	0	0	0	\N	0	0	0	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	0	0	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	2025-11-17 12:34:36.664	2025-11-17 12:35:54.369	0	\N	\N	\N	[{"data": "# Context Exploration Report - ST-2\\n\\n## Story: Comprehensive Agent Statistics Tracking System\\n\\n## Relevant Files Identified\\n\\n### Core OTEL Infrastructure (NEW - ST-2)\\n- `backend/src/services/otel-ingestion.service.ts` - OTEL event ingestion and processing\\n- `backend/src/services/metrics-aggregation.service.ts` - Metrics aggregation for ComponentRun\\n- `backend/prisma/schema.prisma` - OtelEvent model and ComponentRun extensions\\n\\n### MCP Metrics Tools (NEW - ST-2)\\n- `backend/src/mcp/servers/metrics/get_component_actual_metrics.ts` - Query component metrics\\n- `backend/src/mcp/servers/metrics/get_workflow_metrics_breakdown.ts` - Workflow-level aggregation\\n- `backend/src/mcp/servers/metrics/get_agent_interaction_history.ts` - Detailed OTEL event history\\n\\n### Existing Metrics Infrastructure\\n- `backend/src/agent-metrics/` - Agent performance analytics (DTOs, service, controller)\\n- `backend/src/metrics/` - General metrics service\\n- `backend/src/code-metrics/` - Code quality metrics\\n\\n### Workflow Execution (Integration Points)\\n- `backend/src/execution/workflow-state.service.ts` - Uses ComponentRun model\\n- `backend/src/mcp/servers/execution/record_component_complete.ts` - Records metrics on completion\\n- `backend/src/mcp/servers/execution/get_workflow_context.ts` - Returns aggregated metrics\\n\\n## Key Patterns Found\\n\\n### ComponentRun Schema (15+ new fields)\\n```typescript\\n// Session Tracking\\nsessionId: String  // Maps to OTEL session\\n\\n// Cache Metrics\\ntokensCacheRead, tokensCacheWrite, cacheHits, cacheMisses, cacheHitRate\\n\\n// Code Impact\\nlinesAdded, linesDeleted, linesModified\\ncomplexityBefore, complexityAfter\\ncoverageBefore, coverageAfter\\n\\n// Quality Metrics\\nerrorRate, successRate, toolBreakdown (JSON)\\n\\n// Performance\\ncostBreakdown (JSON), modelId, temperature, timeToFirstToken, tokensPerSecond\\n```\\n\\n### OtelEvent Model (NEW)\\n- Links to ComponentRun via sessionId or componentRunId\\n- Stores raw OTEL events from Claude Code\\n- Fields: eventType, toolName, toolParameters, toolDuration, toolSuccess\\n- Processed flag for aggregation state\\n\\n## Dependencies Map\\n\\n```\\nOtelIngestionService\\n  ├─ PrismaClient (OtelEvent, ComponentRun)\\n  └─ Logger utility\\n\\nMetricsAggregationService\\n  ├─ PrismaClient\\n  ├─ OtelIngestionService (event data)\\n  └─ ComponentRun model (target for aggregation)\\n\\nMCP Metrics Tools\\n  ├─ ComponentRun queries (Prisma)\\n  ├─ OtelEvent queries\\n  └─ WorkflowRun context\\n```\\n\\n## Technical Constraints\\n\\n1. **Database Migrations Pending** - 3 migrations not applied:\\n   - 20251110141007_update_story_status_enum\\n   - 20251111093052_add_layers_and_components\\n   - 20251112135506_agent_workflow_mvp\\n\\n2. **No Ingestion API Endpoint** - OtelIngestionService exists but no HTTP controller to receive events from Claude Code\\n\\n3. **Session Correlation Gap** - Need mechanism to inject workflow metadata into Claude Code telemetry via OTEL_RESOURCE_ATTRIBUTES\\n\\n4. **OTEL Collector Not Configured** - No Docker/infrastructure setup for receiving OTEL data\\n\\n## Implementation Recommendations\\n\\n1. **Priority 1: Apply Database Migrations**\\n   - Run `prisma migrate deploy` to create OtelEvent table and ComponentRun extensions\\n\\n2. **Priority 2: Create OTEL Ingestion Controller**\\n   - POST /api/otel/events endpoint\\n   - Integrate with OtelIngestionService\\n\\n3. **Priority 3: Configure OTEL Collector**\\n   - Docker container with routing to our backend\\n   - Configure Claude Code to export telemetry\\n\\n4. **Priority 4: Implement Session Mapping**\\n   - Pass OTEL_RESOURCE_ATTRIBUTES when spawning agents\\n   - Include workflow_run_id and component_run_id\\n\\n5. **Priority 5: Dashboard Integration**\\n   - Frontend components for live metrics display\\n   - Real-time updates via WebSocket or polling\\n", "size": 3737, "s3Key": "workflow-runs/81567f3d-3765-463a-be99-56370c51b42f/components/89e6cc43-7bcb-41aa-9173-3dcd1c9cfa46/context-exploration-st2.md", "format": "markdown", "filename": "context-exploration-st2.md", "language": null, "mimeType": "application/markdown", "uploadedAt": "2025-11-17T12:35:22.575Z", "artifactType": "report"}]
45a4c864-6ec5-4685-ad42-dcfe9df26663	81567f3d-3765-463a-be99-56370c51b42f	42d40d84-83e0-436d-a813-00bea87ff98b	\N	completed	f	{"contextExploration": "20+ files identified, 4 critical gaps, session correlation via OTEL_RESOURCE_ATTRIBUTES"}	{"risks": 4, "successMetrics": 4, "useCasesLinked": 5, "acceptanceCriteria": 6}	\N	0	0	4200	39	\N	1	\N	\N	{}	{}	\N	\N	\N	\N	0	1	0	[]	\N	0	0	0	0	\N	0	0	0	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	0	0	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	2025-11-17 12:36:06.373	2025-11-17 12:36:56.799	0	\N	\N	\N	[{"data": "# Business Analysis Report - ST-2\\n\\n## Stakeholders\\n- **Product Owner**: Needs visibility into agent performance and cost efficiency\\n- **Development Team**: Requires actionable metrics for optimization\\n- **Operations**: Needs monitoring and alerting on agent health\\n- **Finance**: Cost tracking and budget forecasting\\n\\n## Refined Requirements\\n\\n### Must Have (P0)\\n1. **Session Correlation** - Map Claude Code sessions to workflow component runs\\n2. **OTEL Event Ingestion** - Receive and store all Claude Code telemetry\\n3. **Metrics Aggregation** - Calculate KPIs from raw events\\n4. **Database Schema** - Persist all metrics in ComponentRun\\n\\n### Should Have (P1)\\n5. **Real-time Updates** - Live metrics during agent execution\\n6. **Dashboard Visualization** - Grafana/frontend integration\\n7. **Cost Calculation** - Automatic USD cost computation\\n\\n### Could Have (P2)\\n8. **Alerting** - Threshold-based notifications\\n9. **Comparison Tools** - Agent vs Agent performance\\n10. **Historical Trends** - Time-series analysis\\n\\n## Acceptance Criteria\\n\\n### AC-1: OTEL Event Ingestion\\n**Given** Claude Code is running with telemetry enabled\\n**When** it emits an OTEL event (api_request, tool_result, etc.)\\n**Then** the event is stored in OtelEvent table with session_id, event_type, and attributes\\n\\n### AC-2: Session-to-ComponentRun Mapping\\n**Given** a workflow component run is started\\n**When** OTEL_RESOURCE_ATTRIBUTES includes component_run_id\\n**Then** all OTEL events from that session are linked to the ComponentRun\\n\\n### AC-3: Cache Metrics Calculation\\n**Given** OTEL events contain token cache information\\n**When** metrics aggregation runs\\n**Then** ComponentRun.cacheHitRate = cacheHits / (cacheHits + cacheMisses)\\n\\n### AC-4: Tool Breakdown Aggregation\\n**Given** multiple tool_result events for a component run\\n**When** aggregation completes\\n**Then** toolBreakdown JSON contains per-tool stats: {calls, errors, avgDuration}\\n\\n### AC-5: Cost Breakdown Calculation\\n**Given** API request events with token counts\\n**When** cost calculation runs\\n**Then** costBreakdown = {input: $, output: $, cache: $} in USD\\n\\n### AC-6: Code Impact Tracking\\n**Given** an agent modifies code files\\n**When** execution completes\\n**Then** linesAdded, linesDeleted, linesModified are populated\\n\\n## Risk Assessment\\n\\n| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |\\n|------|-----------|--------|------------|\\n| Database migration fails | Medium | High | Create backup before migration |\\n| OTEL events overwhelm storage | Medium | Medium | Batch processing, retention policy |\\n| Session correlation misses events | High | High | Validate OTEL_RESOURCE_ATTRIBUTES injection |\\n| Cost calculation inaccurate | Low | Medium | Use official Claude pricing API |\\n\\n## Success Metrics\\n\\n1. **Data Completeness**: 95%+ of component runs have complete metrics\\n2. **Ingestion Latency**: <1s from event emission to storage\\n3. **Aggregation Accuracy**: Cost breakdown sums match total cost ±0.01%\\n4. **Query Performance**: Dashboard loads in <2s with 10K+ events\\n", "size": 3004, "s3Key": "workflow-runs/81567f3d-3765-463a-be99-56370c51b42f/components/42d40d84-83e0-436d-a813-00bea87ff98b/ba-analysis-st2.md", "format": "markdown", "filename": "ba-analysis-st2.md", "language": null, "mimeType": "application/markdown", "uploadedAt": "2025-11-17T12:36:44.840Z", "artifactType": "report"}]
