ted metrics\\n- Real-time updates via incremental aggregation\\n\\n## No Additional Architecture Changes Required\\nThe existing architectAnalysis is comprehensive and ready for implementation.\\n", "size": 1603, "s3Key": "workflow-runs/81567f3d-3765-463a-be99-56370c51b42f/components/24661ab0-8fb8-4194-870c-40de12ea77b7/architecture-validation-st2.md", "format": "markdown", "filename": "architecture-validation-st2.md", "language": null, "mimeType": "application/markdown", "uploadedAt": "2025-11-17T12:38:46.991Z", "artifactType": "report"}]
