. Prisma client not regenerated\\n3. Missing test database setup\\n\\n## Recommendations\\n\\n1. **Apply migrations before running tests**\\n2. **Regenerate Prisma client**: `npx prisma generate`\\n3. **Set up test database** with OtelEvent table\\n4. **Add integration tests** for HTTP ingestion endpoint\\n5. **Add E2E tests** for complete OTEL pipeline\\n\\n## Quality Assessment\\n\\n- **Unit test coverage**: High (services and MCP tools)\\n- **Integration test coverage**: Low (no controller tests)\\n- **E2E test coverage**: None (pipeline not tested)\\n- **Total test code**: ~75K+ lines across all files\\n", "size": 1969, "s3Key": "workflow-runs/81567f3d-3765-463a-be99-56370c51b42f/components/0e54a24e-5cc8-4bef-ace8-bb33be6f1679/qa-validation-st2.md", "format": "markdown", "filename": "qa-validation-st2.md", "language": null, "mimeType": "application/markdown", "uploadedAt": "2025-11-17T12:41:04.015Z", "artifactType": "test_results"}]
