rvices not wired into app.module.ts\\n- Need OtelModule with providers\\n\\n### 3. Session ID Extraction\\n- No utility to extract session ID from Claude Code process\\n- Needed for agent spawning integration\\n\\n## Technical Debt\\n\\n1. **Error handling** - Services lack comprehensive try/catch\\n2. **Validation** - No DTO validation for incoming events\\n3. **Rate limiting** - No protection against event flood\\n4. **Logging** - Uses custom Logger, not NestJS Logger\\n\\n## Total Implementation: 1,723 lines of production code\\n", "size": 1878, "s3Key": "workflow-runs/81567f3d-3765-463a-be99-56370c51b42f/components/b8734895-1ecb-4f22-bba4-b9d04d66222b/implementation-status-st2.md", "format": "markdown", "filename": "implementation-status-st2.md", "language": "typescript", "mimeType": "application/markdown", "uploadedAt": "2025-11-17T12:39:39.572Z", "artifactType": "code"}]
