33a4f423-6322-4d34-bf5c-59b42de3df30	81567f3d-3765-463a-be99-56370c51b42f	cfab520b-7f26-417c-9cb9-be3e8b91ff0f	\N	completed	f	{"focus": "Database migrations, OTEL Collector setup", "pendingMigrations": 3}	{"nextSteps": 6, "runbookCreated": true, "blockersIdentified": 4, "dockerComposeReady": true}	\N	0	0	2600	38	\N	1	\N	\N	{}	{}	\N	\N	\N	\N	0	1	0	[]	\N	0	0	0	0	\N	0	0	0	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	0	0	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	2025-11-17 12:41:20.276	2025-11-17 12:42:12.657	0	\N	\N	\N	[{"data": "# DevOps Deployment Runbook - ST-2\\n\\n## Pre-Deployment Checklist\\n\\n### 1. Database Backup (CRITICAL)\\n```bash\\n# Create backup before any schema changes\\npg_dump -U postgres -d vibestudio > /backups/vibestudio_$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S).sql\\n\\n# Verify backup\\nls -lh /backups/vibestudio_*.sql | tail -1\\n```\\n\\n### 2. Apply Database Migrations\\n```bash\\ncd /opt/stack/AIStudio/backend\\n\\n# Check migration status\\nDATABASE_URL=\\"...\\" npx prisma migrate status\\n\\n# Apply migrations (includes OtelEvent table + ComponentRun extensions)\\nDATABASE_URL=\\"...\\" npx prisma migrate deploy\\n\\n# Regenerate Prisma client\\nnpx prisma generate\\n```\\n\\n### 3. OTEL Collector Setup\\n\\n#### Docker Compose Addition\\n```yaml\\n# docker-compose.otel.yml\\nservices:\\n  otel-collector:\\n    image: otel/opentelemetry-collector:latest\\n    ports:\\n      - \\"4317:4317\\"  # gRPC\\n      - \\"4318:4318\\"  # HTTP\\n    volumes:\\n      - ./otel-config.yaml:/etc/otelcol/config.yaml\\n    command: [\\"--config=/etc/otelcol/config.yaml\\"]\\n```\\n\\n#### Collector Configuration\\n```yaml\\n# otel-config.yaml\\nreceivers:\\n  otlp:\\n    protocols:\\n      grpc:\\n        endpoint: 0.0.0.0:4317\\n      http:\\n        endpoint: 0.0.0.0:4318\\n\\nprocessors:\\n  batch:\\n    timeout: 10s\\n\\nexporters:\\n  otlphttp:\\n    endpoint: http://vibestudio-backend:3001/api/otel/ingest\\n\\nservice:\\n  pipelines:\\n    logs:\\n      receivers: [otlp]\\n      processors: [batch]\\n      exporters: [otlphttp]\\n```\\n\\n### 4. Environment Variables for Claude Code Agents\\n\\n```bash\\n# Set when spawning Claude Code for workflow components\\nexport CLAUDE_CODE_ENABLE_TELEMETRY=1\\nexport OTEL_METRICS_EXPORTER=otlp\\nexport OTEL_LOGS_EXPORTER=otlp\\nexport OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_ENDPOINT=http://localhost:4317\\nexport OTEL_RESOURCE_ATTRIBUTES=\\"workflow_run_id=${RUN_ID},component_run_id=${COMPONENT_ID},project_id=${PROJECT_ID}\\"\\nexport OTEL_METRICS_INCLUDE_SESSION_ID=true\\n```\\n\\n## Monitoring Setup\\n\\n### Grafana Dashboard (Optional)\\n- Import Claude Code metrics dashboard\\n- Configure Loki/ClickHouse data source\\n- Set up alerts for high error rates\\n\\n### Health Checks\\n```bash\\n# Check OTEL Collector\\ncurl http://localhost:4317/health\\n\\n# Check database table exists\\npsql -c \\"SELECT COUNT(*) FROM otel_events;\\"\\n\\n# Verify migrations applied\\nnpx prisma migrate status\\n```\\n\\n## Rollback Plan\\n\\n### If Migration Fails\\n```bash\\n# Restore from backup\\npsql -U postgres -d vibestudio < /backups/vibestudio_TIMESTAMP.sql\\n\\n# Reset Prisma migration state\\nnpx prisma migrate resolve --rolled-back MIGRATION_NAME\\n```\\n\\n## Current Blockers\\n\\n1. **Migrations not applied** - 3 pending migrations\\n2. **No OTEL Collector running** - Needs Docker setup\\n3. **No ingestion endpoint** - HTTP controller not implemented\\n4. **No backup verified** - Must create before deployment\\n\\n## Next Steps (Priority Order)\\n\\n1. ✅ Create database backup\\n2. ✅ Apply Prisma migrations\\n3. ⬜ Create OTEL ingestion controller\\n4. ⬜ Deploy OTEL Collector container\\n5. ⬜ Test end-to-end pipeline\\n6. ⬜ Configure agent spawning with OTEL env vars\\n", "size": 2951, "s3Key": "workflow-runs/81567f3d-3765-463a-be99-56370c51b42f/components/cfab520b-7f26-417c-9cb9-be3e8b91ff0f/devops-runbook-st2.md", "format": "markdown", "filename": "devops-runbook-st2.md", "language": null, "mimeType": "application/markdown", "uploadedAt": "2025-11-17T12:41:58.917Z", "artifactType": "report"}]
