421a755d-541e-47de-a084-2b433f8a2ca4	6ac348ee-69d7-4592-93d5-bdcab5a9c5a2	b8734895-1ecb-4f22-bba4-b9d04d66222b	\N	completed	f	{"task": "Create OTEL ingestion HTTP controller and NestJS module"}	{"endpoints": 4, "linesOfCode": 496, "filesCreated": 5, "buildSuccessful": true}	\N	0	0	8500	181	\N	1	496	\N	{}	{}	\N	\N	\N	\N	0	1	0	[]	\N	0	0	0	0	\N	0	0	0	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	0	0	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	2025-11-17 12:48:10.921	2025-11-17 12:52:02.569	0	\N	\N	\N	[{"data": "# OTEL Ingestion Implementation - ST-2\\n\\n## Files Created\\n\\n### 1. `/backend/src/otel/dto/otel-event.dto.ts`\\nDTOs for OTEL event validation:\\n- `OtelEventDto` - Single event structure with validation decorators\\n- `OtelBatchIngestDto` - Batch ingestion\\n- `OtelResourceAttributesDto` - Workflow metadata\\n- `OtelIngestResponseDto` - API response structure\\n\\n### 2. `/backend/src/otel/otel.controller.ts`\\nNestJS HTTP controller with endpoints:\\n- `POST /api/otel/ingest` - Single event ingestion\\n- `POST /api/otel/ingest/batch` - Batch event ingestion\\n- `POST /api/otel/session/map` - Map session to component run\\n- `POST /api/otel/aggregate/:componentRunId` - Trigger aggregation\\n\\nFeatures:\\n- Resource attributes parsing from headers\\n- Automatic workflow metadata extraction\\n- Request logging\\n- Error handling\\n\\n### 3. `/backend/src/otel/otel.service.ts`\\nService layer with comprehensive functionality:\\n- `ingestEvent()` - Store OTEL event with session correlation\\n- `mapSessionToComponentRun()` - Link session to component\\n- `aggregateComponentMetrics()` - Calculate KPIs from events\\n- `updateComponentMetrics()` - Real-time metric updates\\n\\nMetrics aggregated:\\n- Token usage (input/output/cache)\\n- Tool breakdown (calls, errors, avgDuration)\\n- Cache hit/miss rates\\n- Error and success rates\\n\\n### 4. `/backend/src/otel/otel.module.ts`\\nNestJS module registration:\\n- Imports PrismaModule\\n- Registers controller and service\\n- Exports OtelService for other modules\\n\\n### 5. Updated `/backend/src/app.module.ts`\\n- Added OtelModule import\\n- Registered in module imports array\\n\\n## API Endpoints Available\\n\\n```\\nPOST /api/otel/ingest\\nPOST /api/otel/ingest/batch\\nPOST /api/otel/session/map\\nPOST /api/otel/aggregate/:componentRunId\\n```\\n\\n## Total Lines of Code: ~450 lines\\n", "size": 1751, "s3Key": "workflow-runs/6ac348ee-69d7-4592-93d5-bdcab5a9c5a2/components/b8734895-1ecb-4f22-bba4-b9d04d66222b/otel-implementation-summary.md", "format": "markdown", "filename": "otel-implementation-summary.md", "language": "typescript", "mimeType": "application/markdown", "uploadedAt": "2025-11-17T12:51:45.996Z", "artifactType": "code"}]
